me":"2018-09-02T01:06:18.000Z","msg":"嫌樓價高物價貴走向廣州？未聽過北上廣？ 人工低生活成本高 仲慘撚過香港喎 申請個班人係咪訓天橋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69775c328017689b23b906e739f8c37865e482b7","tid":802908,"uid":43133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T01:06:35.000Z","msg":"呢班垃圾本身都住支那喺支那打工架啦, 喺支那申請埋做隻正式支那豬有何「踴躍北上」可言？"},{"pid":"32db898761cf6f28ca8fde9cb74a18e0d6681571","tid":802908,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T01:24:35.000Z","msg":"記住剪埋張hkid"},{"pid":"61182a8a6c1b1d3e00db0596a5a7133d95c9cbcb","tid":802908,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T01:25:55.000Z","msg":"果D 係咪諗住瞞稅"},{"pid":"bfee646f9bab2f996d64fcca1c142d9bc7193d3a","tid":802908,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T01:44:14.000Z","msg":"唔好笑<br />\n<br />\n清洗香港<br />\n<br />\n先清走d低端人口"},{"pid":"2c229266f4215908a588d0ceaa547e0feed1722d","tid":802908,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T01:52:01.000Z","msg":"應該要香港班北上搵人仔的偽人強制申請，仲要交重稅，追溯期起碼由20年前計起"}]}